        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "\n$y=m x+b$ \n\nslope  m and y axis intercept b \nderivative of $y=a x^{n}+b$ with respect to x:\n\n$d y/d x=a\\;n\\;x^{(n-1)}$ \n\nBecause b is a constant - think of it as $b x^{0}-i t s$ 1\nderivative is $0b x^{-1}=0$ \n\nFor a straight line,$a=m{\\mathrm{~a n d~}}n=1{\\mathrm{~s o~}}$ \n$\\mathrm{d}\\mathsf{y}/\\mathrm{d}\\mathsf{x}=m1~x^{(0)}$ ,or because $x^{0}=1$ ,\n\n$d y/d x=m$ \n\n",
          "block_bbox": [
